User opens the application.
System displays the starting screen.
User clicks on "Create an Account" button.
System displays the “Create Account” form.
User inputs their email.
System verifies that the email is valid.
System asks the user to create a password.
User inputs a password twice.
System verifies if the passwords match.
User selects the “Create Account” button.
System generates a 3-digit ID number for the user.
System displays the ID number on the screen.
Users click “OK” to confirm the ID number.
System saves the new account data to the database.

Alternate/Exceptional Flows:
6a. If the email is not valid or already in use, the system provides an error message.
8a. If the passwords don’t match, the system provides an error message.